oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sleepy LeBeef Live at the Lone Star Cafe - 1978-10-02
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is from the Lone Star Café live show. The tape features a live performance of Sleepy LeBeef (musician). The Lone Star Café show is presented by Mort Cooperman, Bill McGivney and the WHN radio network. The recording of Sleepy LeBeef is from October 02, 1978.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Sleepy LeBeef
